rawContent:
“I’m sorry” I say
Again
A slick slithering poison
From my mouth to your veins
“It’s okay”
You say

Not rebuked
Never forgiven 

One day
I hope the poison 
Is potent enough 
To make that part of you
That cares for me
Die

#poem #poetry #depression
